headline: Strength Seen in Itron (ITRI): Can Its 3.7% Jump Turn into More Strength?
summary: Itron (ITRI) witnessed a jump in share price last session on above-average trading volume. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions for the stock doesn't suggest further strength down the road.
